About
=====

This torrent was not made by Impact Team, but it is a collection of their 3
dumps released about Ashley Madison. Advantages over the original torrents:

- It saves a lot of disk space (if you use other OS than Linux, make sure
  **SquashFS** with **xz** compression is supported).
- Only 1 torrent with all 3 dumps;
- No corrupted files or incomplete downloads;
- Content reorganized in 4 files:
    - Documents;
    - Database dumps;
    - Repositories (git);
    - CEO e-mails;

Differences from Impact Team's releases
=======================================

- SquashFS, a highly compressed read-only filesystem for Linux:
    - Better compression;
    - No need for decompression (check SquashFS instructions below);
- Git optimization (git gc --aggressive) to reduce repositories' size;
- `noel.biderman.mail.7z`:
    - Removed corrupted file from 2nd dump;
    - Although the 3rd dump was incomplete (torrent stuck in 93.3%),
      the completed part of the file is found extracted here.

SquashFS
========

Instructions on how to mount SquashFS volumes follow.

Requirements
------------
Only 2 packages are required (names vary across Linux distributions):

- `squashfs-tools` (version 4.3 used)
- `xz-utils` (or simply `xz`, version 5.2.1 used)

Example
-------
By default, only root can (un)mount this filesystem, but others can read it:

    $ mkdir ashley_docs
    $ sudo mount -o loop documents.sqsh ashley_docs
    $ ls ashley_docs

That's all, enjoy the files inside `ashley_docs` folder. In the end:

    $ sudo umount ashley_docs

